}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== There would appear to be multiple revisions of this device. This model is presumed to be the v1 model.. but this may be incorrect. It is visible on '''JDI Tech''''s site via [http://web.archive.org/web/20090106181816/http://www.goldxproducts.com/product/show-product.asp?pid=GX3000 archive.org] (grey case, w/ black central portion) and differs from the one [http://www.goldxproducts.com/product/show-product.asp?pid=GX3000 currently on there] (black case, different LED pattern). :The S/N of the hub populating this entry is '''M1000181113'''.
There is no silkscreened text on the board. :The '''[[Cypress Semiconductor]]''' hub IC is marked with "CY7C65640-LFC", "0322 C 04", "CYP 622675", and "KOR".
